'''Mohammad Taghavi''' ({{lang-fa|<U+0645><U+062D><U+0645><U+062F> <U+062A><U+0642><U+0648><U+06CC>}}) is an [[Iran]]ian [[football (soccer)|football]] [[Defender (association football)|defender]], who played for [[Iran national football team|Iran]]. He also played for .<ref>http://www.national-football-teams.com/v2/player.php?id=15999</ref>

